data.description: You've been looking and now you found it !  This excellent condo has a 1st floor primary suite, 2nd floor bed & bath PLUS a loft area perfect for your home office. You will enjoy the fully equipped kitchen with stainless steel appliances and a breakfast area.  The garage comes with an with opener and the condo exterior is low maintenance.  All this is affordably priced and located in a quiet, well maintained, conveniently located neighborhood.  Don't wait call - your agent today for an appointment or come by Sunday April 14 between 1pm - 3pm to tour the Open House.
